          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A stack of pure 93Nb of thickness 10.5 mg/cm2",
                " (measured by the alpha-transmission method) were",
                " fastened to an aluminum frame, having a circular hole",
                " of diameter 1.2 cm in the center backed by an Al-",
                " catcher of thickness 2 mg/cm2."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Pre-calibrated CANBERA's HPGe detector coupled",
                " to the Ortec's PC-based multi-channel analyzer"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STTA",
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BCINT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The incident flux of the alpha-beam was",
                " determined from the charge collected in the Faraday",
                " Cup, as well as from the counts of the two charge",
                " integrators.",
                "A copper foil of thickness 10.68 mg/cm2 was also used",
                " as a flux monitor."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": 16.0,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The overall error in the measured",
                " cross section is found to be less than 16%.",
                "Uncertainties in the branching ratio decay constant,",
                " half-lives, etc., have not been taken into account",
                " in the measured cross-sections.",
                "The errors quoted in the production cross-sections",
                " arise mainly  from uncertainties in:",
                " - target thickness",
                " - detector efficiency,",
                " - counting statistics,",
                " - evaluating the gamma-ray intensity and background",
                "   subtraction."
              ]
            },
